{"type": "article", "id": 20299, "title": "木桌系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134103DfkhALX26FcgE53G.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国建筑师 David Chipperfield 曾为德国家具品牌 e15 设计过木质家具，这是新发布的改良版。咖啡桌的由两片向外倾斜的木板做支撑，中间有一根横梁，与桌面保持垂直，整体是左右对称的，简洁而大方。设计师通过这个概念设计了靠墙的桌子和凳子，调整了长宽比例，很典雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071341018KxeGPNrW4D6aBIu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134101glxuP2qfKn9EDmes.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11324786\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134102xQc4z1UyhFSI7O62.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.30555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134102VBzPjoNnXMZIe7tL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63034188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}